    {
      "id": "c3dd2f4e-f466-4f84-9715-6f872728c4c0",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 18,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "7b80bf5b-1dce-4fc9-b8be-73b2cb7ed900",
          "type": "song",
          "songId": "a0c37c13-4a36-4e2d-b8b5-1179a58bc65e"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "1022f29c-abeb-4025-99e0-f6b52cef0cca",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 16,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "8879ef48-9128-4674-b2d9-71511d6ff2e7",
          "text": "Matapos ihayag ng Diyos ang Kanyang Salita, tayo ay tinatawag na tumugon sa pananampalataya at pagsunod.",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": false,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "aa6bce9b-fbff-4c39-9f7a-dd3a0b25d3fb",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 17,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "1731e2e4-79e8-4f3f-abcc-a484cb389d5b",
          "text": "Ngayon sa makapangyarihang gumawa ng lubhang sagana ng higit sa lahat ng ating hinihingi o iniisip, ayon sa kapangyarihang gumagawa sa atin, Ay sumakaniya nawa ang kaluwalhatian sa iglesia at kay Cristo Jesus sa buong panahon magpakailan man. Siya nawa.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "Ephesians 3:20–21",
          "amenExpected": false,
          "trinitarianSeal": "fil"
        },
        {
          "id": "c20c4776-b08a-4631-b684-97e8d2ccb100",
          "type": "formula",
          "formulaId": "8e6d1c8d-e83d-4341-9242-45b3c7389bf9",
          "visibility": "both",
          "overrideText": null
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "7bde178d-29f5-4d6c-b084-fd8521c44a31",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 1,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "6547c879-f3d3-4c65-9650-ea56ec68af92",
          "text": "Dinggin mo ang dalangin ko Oh Panginoon; pakinggan mo ang aking mga pamanhik: sa iyong pagtatapat ay sagutin mo ako, at sa iyong katuwiran.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "Mga Awit 143:1",
          "amenExpected": false
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e7e0f903-846f-46a2-86da-5c815411c078",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 7,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "5fb5db50-396f-4fc5-84a6-a9adaa57a75e",
          "text": "Na siya rin ang nagdala ng ating mga kasalanan sa kaniyang katawan sa ibabaw ng kahoy, upang pagkamatay natin sa mga kasalanan, ay mangabuhay tayo sa katuwiran; na dahil sa kaniyang mga sugat ay nangagsigaling kayo.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "1 Peter 2:24",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "800cd55c-4083-40e0-be11-fbd6dfa65c7c",
          "type": "formula",
          "marks": [],
          "formulaId": "a94ae276-3518-4dd3-8c7b-6aa8a1c7045c",
          "visibility": "both",
          "overrideText": "Sumasampalataya ba kayo sa ebanghelyong ito?\nSumasampalataya po kami.\nKung gayon, sa pangalan ni Cristo, at sa awtoridad ng Kaniyang Salita, habang kayo’y nagpapatotoo sa inyong sariling paniniwala sa ebanghelyo, ipinahahayag ng Kasulatan sa inyo na ang inyong mga kasalanan ay pinatawad na, at kayo’y wala na sa ilalim ng kaparusahan ng Diyos.",
          "trinitarianSeal": "fil"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "798c0990-0cb8-4321-aba2-dc4c7a786546",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 4,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "190e7562-874c-44cb-bcef-6468975045e3",
          "text": "If we say we have no sin, we deceive ourselves, and the truth is not in us. If we confess our sins, He is faithful and just to forgive us our sins and to cleanse us from all unrighteousness.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "1 John 1:8–9",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "3b9c045b-4534-4d53-9f36-d29b18cbf659",
          "text": "Nasaksihan natin ang kabanalan at kadakilan ng Diyos sa Kanyang mga salmo at sa Kanyang kautusan. Ngayo’y tinatawag naman tayo upang magsisi sa ating mga kasalanan. Pakinggan natin ang panawagan sa atin sa [Text]:",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "edd03b21-63d3-4f64-9e53-fd1eed91d1bb",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 4,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "250f8d94-ba43-4926-93e7-bd8e75bc594e",
          "text": "If You, O Lord, kept track of iniquities, then who, O Lord, could stand? But with You there is forgiveness, so that You may be feared.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [
            {
              "end": 14,
              "type": "small_caps",
              "start": 10
            }
          ],
          "citation": "Psalms 130:3–4",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e9d5f867-acf9-433f-a08e-fa42caceac58",
      "liturgy_id": "774b3e8e-6aa8-4c91-b7b7-176c5ed30d62",
      "template_section_index": 3,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "3457c09f-b287-4c06-a2b9-bc9e34b5ba04",
          "text": "At sinalita ng Dios ang lahat ng salitang ito, na sinasabi, Ako ang Panginoon mong Dios, na naglabas sa iyo sa lupain ng Egipto, sa bahay ng pagkaalipin:\n**1   Huwag kang magkakaroon ng ibang mga dios sa harap ko.\n2   Huwag kang gagawa para sa iyo ng anomang diyus-diyosan.\n3   Huwag mong babanggitin ang pangalan ng Panginoon mong Dios sa walang kabuluhan;\n4   Alalahanin mo ang araw ng sabbath upang ipangilin. \n5   Igalang mo ang iyong ama at ang iyong ina.\n6   Huwag kang papatay.\n7   Huwag kang mangangalunya.\n8   Huwag kang magnanakaw.\n9   Huwag kang magsinungaling laban sa iyong kapuwa.\n10   Huwag mong iimbutin ang anomang bagay ng iyong kapuwa.**",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "Exodo 20:1–17",
          "translation": "fil",
          "amenExpected": false
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "17736296-cba6-4e52-8d3d-7be98f1f1495",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 15,
      "items": [],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "053072b2-9c9c-4fe0-8542-02f3bcd0fc92",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 6,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "35e1ee0b-a793-4462-a112-b49f8e4105df",
          "text": "Ating awitin ang [Salmo/Himno] bilang isang panalangin at pagpapahayag ng kaligtasan na mayroon kay Cristo na ating Panginoon.",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        },
        {
          "id": "21df5bbb-67f0-41fc-971e-44c983bc3b90",
          "type": "song",
          "songId": "90ef6c6c-f7d7-4d0c-a0e7-182a613aabfd"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "be235f4e-fc2f-4d8a-85e1-0803d21c63b1",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 1,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "8a71e62b-7889-4c8c-8f2f-14a2e2611066",
          "text": "Hear my prayer, O God;\nlisten to the words of my mouth.\nSurely God is my helper;\nthe Lord is the sustainer of my soul.\nFreely I will sacrifice to You;\nI will praise Your name, O LORD,\nfor it is good.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [
            {
              "end": 199,
              "type": "congregation",
              "start": 56
            }
          ],
          "citation": "Psalms 54:2,4,6",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "a8865cb2-5626-4432-9a71-c4432895b9c5",
          "text": "Matapos tayong tawagin ng ating Panginoon upang sambahin Siya, tayo’y manawagan sa Kanyang buháy na Espiritu upang tayo’y makapaghandog ng katanggap-tanggap na pagsamba sa lenggwahe ng [Salmo]:",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "bb4e1e40-b8fb-47a7-9fb2-fb3a5d7a560d",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 11,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "04b8a710-a366-4d59-942d-5dd076e8fd6d",
          "text": "Matapos nating marinig ang pangangaral ng Salita ng Diyos na mamuhay bilang mga Kristiyano ayon sa Espiritu, ating awitin ang [Salmo/Himno] bilang tugon.",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        },
        {
          "id": "baa67d8e-0c34-4a0c-89e1-0d1409ea6a15",
          "type": "song",
          "songId": "bda7965f-c27d-4d49-9ce2-ed549bcd0d3a"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "f445f7ab-4048-4bab-a0ea-5c83b8bb8933",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 18,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "5a13466d-7a51-4db2-aa8e-453b04001084",
          "type": "song",
          "songId": "98eb1a7f-91c8-4523-8e55-84df2f18e696"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "f3e6bb9b-1b3a-438b-a96b-0a2e5cde3782",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 16,
      "items": [],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "8962accd-f21f-4bd1-bc4e-332fb1c081ea",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 14,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "f0ff9046-463b-4ae1-948b-1d5d952f0131",
          "type": "song",
          "songId": "e214aa49-4dcb-40fc-9d9e-156c99584f7e"
        },
        {
          "id": "6fcd0615-b03f-46dc-86de-a7f11265a396",
          "text": "Habang tayo’y nagkakaloob, ating sariwain ang mga kabutihan ng Diyos sa atin sa pagawit ng [Salmo].",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "84d26b42-d065-4542-9e4b-afed78027d75",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 17,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "27dbad66-ce26-4c25-a189-79e138713181",
          "text": "Now to Him who is able to do immeasurably more than all we ask or imagine, according to His power that is at work within us, to Him be the glory in the church and in Christ Jesus throughout all generations, forever and ever. ",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "Ephesians 3:20–21",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false,
          "trinitarianSeal": "en"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "a60e4288-4be8-431e-bf4f-85cb7c2bcd99",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 0,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "0e1a1ded-6303-40fa-a846-b705b4dc367d",
          "text": "Come, let us sing for joy to the LORD;\nlet us shout to the Rock of our salvation!\nLet us enter His presence with thanksgiving;\nlet us make a joyful noise to Him in song.\nFor the LORD is a great God,\na great King above all gods.\nIn His hand are the depths of the earth,\nand the mountain peaks belong to Him.\nThe sea is His, for He made it,\nand His hands formed the dry land.\nO come, let us worship and bow down;\nlet us kneel before the LORD our Maker.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [
            {
              "end": 450,
              "type": "congregation",
              "start": 170
            }
          ],
          "citation": "Psalms 95:1–6",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "88f88744-df6b-4c29-9665-608d0080c709",
          "text": "Pakinggan natin ang panawagan sa atin ng Diyos upang Siya’y sambahin. Ating basahin ang [Salmo]. Ito ang Salita ng Diyos:",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e5acd119-5447-4761-b965-f8e90f3f167d",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 3,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "19e1b192-dda8-4817-aa0f-7d3dcc946587",
          "text": "And God spoke all these words:\nI am the LORD your God,\nwho brought you out of the land of Egypt,\nout of the house of slavery.\n**1   You shall have no other gods before Me.\n2   You shall not make for yourself an idol.\n3   You shall not take the name of the LORD your God in vain.\n4   Remember the Sabbath day by keeping it holy.\n5   Honor your father and mother.\n6   You shall not murder.\n7   You shall not commit adultery.\n8   You shall not steal.\n9   You shall not bear false witness against your neighbor.\n10   You shall not covet anything that belongs to your neighbor.**",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "Exodus 20:1–17",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "34b66958-7c29-45ec-af73-f3e57d05a9ac",
          "text": "Matapos tayong magbigay ng papuri at pagsamba sa ating Diyos, atin namang iharap ang ating mga sarili sa Kanyang Kautusan. Ito ang sinasabi ng Salita ng Diyos:",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "f30a00c1-720b-4e56-b24d-1cb632a154da",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 13,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "d07f975b-814e-493b-8eec-75be4cb7204e",
          "text": "Bilang bahagi ng ating pagsamba sa ating Diyos na buháy, tayo ay magkakaloob. Sa sulat ni [Apostol Pablo] sa [Text], makikita natin ang pangako ng Diyos sa mga nagkakaloob para sa gawain ng Panginoon:",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        },
        {
          "id": "389ac1f4-f9ab-4fe7-a4cb-34f386b83830",
          "text": "Now He who supplies seed to the sower and bread for food will supply and multiply your store of seed and will increase the harvest of your righteousness. You will be enriched in every way to be generous on every occasion, and through us your generosity will produce thanksgiving to God. For this ministry of service is not only supplying the needs of the saints but is also overflowing in many expressions of thanksgiving to God.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "2 Corinthians 9:10–12",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "d7b82206-0108-419b-b828-65fb1c9b41db",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 12,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "c1a39b66-e5d5-4694-aa7b-3f036bccb3d8",
          "text": "Ano ang ating paniniwala at dapat paniwalaan? ",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        },
        {
          "id": "928cf8f2-38bf-4af0-9190-ded912e2dfec",
          "type": "formula",
          "marks": [],
          "formulaId": "a3c2c95f-93c8-49e2-9cf4-addcbe967906",
          "visibility": "both",
          "overrideText": null
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    },
    {
      "id": "e0bb7cad-1f73-4737-ac27-f0b448222130",
      "liturgy_id": "97827c77-f579-4cf1-baf5-925de9be8a15",
      "template_section_index": 7,
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "34fdf6fd-f592-4c11-990d-f11bfa921cb2",
          "text": "Matapos nating ihayag ang ating mga sala sa isang banal na Diyos, atin namang pakinggan ang Kanyang salita na nagpapakita ng katiyakan ng pagpapatawad ng isang maawain at mapagbiyayang Diyos.",
          "type": "verbal_cue",
          "rubric": true,
          "visibility": "leader_only"
        },
        {
          "id": "e85c97e1-2fdf-44f7-88e6-94e0b679cdc1",
          "text": "For God so loved the world that He gave His one and only Son, that everyone who believes in Him shall not perish but have eternal life.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "John 3:16",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "77c8cec7-721c-4076-a0fb-e4284c37b06a",
          "text": "Therefore let it be known to you, brothers, that through Jesus the forgiveness of sins is proclaimed to you. Through Him everyone who believes is justified from everything from which you could not be justified by the law of Moses.",
          "type": "selection",
          "marks": [],
          "citation": "Acts 13:38–39",
          "translation": "en",
          "amenExpected": false
        },
        {
          "id": "895c5b23-51e4-4d12-9ea6-ff7154c298b5",
          "type": "formula",
          "marks": [
            {
              "end": 44,
              "type": "minister",
              "start": 0
            },
            {
              "end": 69,
              "type": "congregation",
              "start": 45
            },
            {
              "end": 344,
              "type": "minister",
              "start": 70
            }
          ],
          "formulaId": "a94ae276-3518-4dd3-8c7b-6aa8a1c7045c",
          "visibility": "both",
          "overrideText": "Sumasampalataya ba kayo sa ebanghelyong ito?\nSumasampalataya po kami.\nKung gayon, sa pangalan ni Cristo, at sa awtoridad ng Kaniyang Salita, habang kayo’y nagpapatotoo sa inyong sariling paniniwala sa ebanghelyo, ipinahahayag ng Kasulatan sa inyo na ang inyong mga kasalanan ay pinatawad na, at kayo’y wala na sa ilalim ng kaparusahan ng Diyos.",
          "trinitarianSeal": "fil"
        }
      ],
      "column_break_before": false
    }
  ]
}